article_title: WSJ New York Photos of the Week, Nov. 9

People photograph the view from the 68th floor of 4 World Trade Center in Manhattan on Wednesday. The 72-story glass tower is the second new building on the Ground Zero site to open since Sept. 11, 2001. Kevin Hagen for The Wall Street Journal
